11
00:01:04,000 --> 00:01:06,600
It's because we're not good role models.

12
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:11,400
In ancient China, there was a grandfather who lived with his son and grandson.

13
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:13,600
They lived together for many years.

14
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:19,000
But the grandfather got old and sick, and the son wanted to get rid of the grandfather.

15
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:22,400
