16
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:28,800
and he carried the grandfather up the mountain with the bamboo basket and wanted to leave him there.

17
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:33,600
The grandson saw the whole situation, so he cleverly said to his dad,

18
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:40,400
Hey dad, that saved the bamboo basket, so I can carry you up the mountain when you become old.

19
00:01:40,400 --> 00:01:47,800
The father was very embarrassed of his behavior, immediately took the grandfather home and took very good care of him.

20
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:52,200
We want to be a good role model who really practice Buddha's Dharma,

21
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:56,200
and be all that is good, that is really honoring Buddha.

22
00:01:56,200 --> 00:02:00,800
Number two is the offering of benefiting all sentient beings.

23
00:02:00,800 --> 00:02:04,800
All sentient beings are Buddha's only beloved son.

24
00:02:04,800 --> 00:02:09,800
So by benefiting all sentient beings, we're making Buddha very happy.

25
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:14,400
And also all sentient beings, they have the same Buddha nature as us.

26
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:16,600
We are all together as one.

27
00:02:16,600 --> 00:02:20,200
So love and really care for all sentient beings.

28
00:02:20,200 --> 00:02:21,200
In America,

29
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:23,200
there was a ten-year-old boy.

30
00:02:23,200 --> 00:02:29,200
