31
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:33,400
So all the teachers got very upset and sent him to the principal's office.

32
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:35,000
And the principal said to him,

33
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:40,000
Clinton, why don't you try to sit on your hands whenever you felt like tapping?

34
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:42,800
But usually that will only work for five seconds.

35
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,800
